{"story":{"group_1":[{"bgm":"bgm03_story07","nameNarration":"月咲","narration":"不知为何，我能从这个竹笛上感到温暖@每次吹奏它，都让我感到治愈","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"吹奏地点，一直是在稍远的神社那里"},{"narration":"我到底算什么人啊……@工房的女仆吗","narrationBg":"bg_adv_12052.jpg"},{"narration":"每当我想要忘记愤怒和悲伤，@心里空落落的时候，@只要一去那个神社，我就能找回自己"},{"narration":"毕竟对我而言，@那个神社是赋予我名字的地方……"},{"narration":"而在前往那个神社的路上，@我也遇见了那个人","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg"},{"narration":"之后给与了我帮助，@为我创造了和月夜再会契机的人"},{"bg":"bg_adv_14043.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":300,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"nameCenter":"月咲","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"唉……@早知道就骑自行车来了。"},{"nameRight":"？？？","textRight":"喂，那边的小姑娘。"},{"chara":[{"id":101901,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"月咲","textCenter":"…………"},{"textRight":"就是你。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":0}],"textCenter":"诶，你叫我？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101601,"motion":200,"pos":2},{"id":101901,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"textRight":"对，没错。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101901}],"textLeft":"你有什么事吗？"},{"chara":[{"id":101601,"motion":1}],"textRight":"我看你非常消沉，@还是小心一些为妙。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101901,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"…………？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":101601}],"textRight":"逢魔，是日夜交替，@天空将坠入黑暗之时。"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":101601}],"textRight":"若是太过消沉，@可是会被魔女吃掉的。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101901}],"textLeft":"诶？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101601,"motion":100}],"textRight":"我是叫你要打起精神。"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5},{"bg":"bg_adv_12052.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101901,"lipSynch":0,"motion":1,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"textCenter":"（刚才那人是怎么回事）","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":101901,"lipSynch":0}],"textCenter":"（被魔女吃掉？）"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":0}],"textCenter":"真奇怪……"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":101801,"motion":0,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"turnChangeIn":"rollInFast","turnChangeOut":"rollOutFast"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":100,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"textCenter":"还是不要想太多吧……","turnChangeIn":"rollInFast","turnChangeOut":"rollOutFast"},{"chara":[{"id":101901,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0}],"textCenter":"…………"},{"chara":[{"id":101901,"lipSynch":0}],"textCenter":"（嗯，好舒服的风……）"},{"chara":[{"id":101901,"lipSynch":0}],"textCenter":"（这样一来，不快的心情@也会随笛声一起被吹走）"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101901,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300}],"textCenter":"…………？"},{"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":101801,"motion":0,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnEffect":"blackFrame"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":400,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"textCenter":"咦？","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":101901}],"textCenter":"刚才……@我和自己擦身而过了？"},{"nameNarration":"月咲","narration":"那肯定是我与@月夜的第一次相遇","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"同时，那也是我们许愿的开始"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"bg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":0,"pos":1,"soulGem":0,"voice":"vo_char_1019_00_08","textHome":"那个女孩，是什么人……和我也太像了点。"}],"nameCenter":"月咲","textCenter":"那个人到底是谁……@和我太像了。","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnEffect":"stop"},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101901,"motion":300}]},{"chara":[{"id":101901}]},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}